snippet.async_client:
import asyncio

from seed import AsyncSeedHttpHead

client = AsyncSeedHttpHead(
    base_url="https://yourhost.com/path/to/api",
)


async def main() -> None:
    await client.user.list(
        limit=1,
    )


asyncio.run(main())
